      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a fantastic driving experience with this well-maintained vehicle! It's in good condition, showing pride of ownership and a history of careful use. This reliable ride is perfect for anyone seeking a blend of quality and value, ready to take on the road with confidence. Come see why this dependable car is the perfect fit for your next journey!",
